U.S. Representative Peter Roskam, a 
Republican from  Illinois , discusses his proposed tax 
legislation and the prospects of New Jersey Governor Chris 
Christie entering the 2012 presidential race.   Roskam speaks with Betty Liu on Bloomberg Television's `In 
the Loop.' (Source: Bloomberg)   Running Time: 05:46
 